{"tid":176484,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"公司想整新價錢牌，想問點樣可以link到產品data去價錢牌template?","createTime":"2017-03-28T08:14:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-28T12:10:30.000Z","uid":13581,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3b12bce699810585f4e6dd787c00d4e012a27e76","tid":176484,"uid":13581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T08:14:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/28/161025_a71036cd5ae4baf23b468095f812d419.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F28%2F161025_a71036cd5ae4baf23b468095f812d419.jpg&h=102e20bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n公司想整以上呢個價錢牌<br />\n<br />\n本身有個excel data base，入面有曬個價錢牌template既所有資料，想問點樣可以唔洗人手copy and paste咁樣整落個價錢牌到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：乜都唔識，而且公司係細鋪頭仔，但想個形象好d，所以想整個有系統既價錢牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9357b1c175af41a5eaa844338206a8aeaef3a177","tid":176484,"uid":33216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T08:17:28.000Z","msg":"用word的合併列印，data放excel"},{"pid":"616de3cdfa5a0b8138ee3dab45c908ec0cb20e33","tid":176484,"uid":13581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T08:18:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用word的合併列印，data放excel</blockquote><br />\n唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可唔可以講多小小<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91e1080a58e8e2dc2d104c303c47a4dca95cd518","tid":176484,"uid":48623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T08:20:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>用word的合併列印，data放excel</blockquote><br />\n唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可唔可以講多小小<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://bfy.tw/AtOY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2